skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: enacomm banking
des: The Enacomm Banking Skill provides financial institution customers with a number of self-service functions including account balance, transaction history, branch locations, CD rates, transfer funds, make a payment, loan information, and credit card information. Users select the financial institution and provide account authentication credentials at the time of skill linking. Please note that financial information may be read aloud or displayed visually.
